section.section:
"Hazardous materials" includes any grouping or classification of materials, that the United States Secretary of Transportation designates as a hazardous material, including:
Explosives;
Radioactive materials;
Etiologic agents;
Flammable liquids or solids;
Combustible liquids or solids;
Poisons;
Oxidizing or corrosive materials; and
Compressed gases.
